       <h3><b> About GIST </b></h3>
       <h5 style="text-align:justify"><h5>The GIST app improves your grocery shopping experience. </h5>
        <i>How?</i><br>
        <p style="text-align:justify">    
        It helps you become more efficient, and GIST approaches the issue of efficiency in a novel way. This app takes the perspective from the psychological phenomenon “planning fallacy”, which states that people have a great tendency to underestimate the time needed to complete a certain task. <br><br>
        <i>What can GIST do exactly?</i><br>
        With GIST, you can combat this fallacy by keeping smart lists and tracking your own grocery shopping behavior.  Your inputed grocery list is automatically rearranged according to the specified market so that you can efficiently shop without going back and forth in the market. Whenever you go shopping, you can log your estimated amount of time, actual time taken, your mood and hunger level. When you are finished, your purchased items will be recorded. <br><br>
        This data is used for your personal trends and statistic which is a powerful tool for you to recognize your habits and use GIST as a means to improve your shopping habits. <br><br>
